  <title>General/Keys preferences</title>
  <para>
    In the <emphasis>General</emphasis> preferences, you can select
    the <emphasis>Keys</emphasis> option to be able to edit the key
    binding for shortcuts in the ITE. Here, you can create your own
    shortcuts or alter the current shortcuts.
  </para>
